{"tid":164592,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"自我實現預言","createTime":"2017-03-20T18:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T05:43:58.000Z","uid":67209,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b92483da6f23f2a59a3837a4d8056d1d303b15","tid":164592,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T18:47:53.000Z","msg":"我信自我實現預言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人覺得自己會成功 就真係會有動力去嘗試 遇到困難會堅持 最後會成功去證明自己既諗法係岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個我地會形容為paradigm <br />\n就係一個固有既諗法 包括覺得你係一個點既人 你會做咩 你對自己既期望係咩<br />\nEg 一個人每日要求自己睇20頁書 就算幾攰佢都會做到 如果病左有日冇睇到 第2日都會補救返 睇返果20頁去達成自己既目標<br />\n但反之 一個人如果覺得自己係垃圾係廢青 做咩都唔會成功 佢就只會繼續係遇到問題既時候逃避<br />\n唔肯嘗試 最後真係失敗左 就真係證明左自己係一個廢青 係一個失敗者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢既paradigm 係覺得自己做咩都唔會成功<br />\n<br />\n每個人都想成功 但唔好再鬧個世界冇比機會你<br />\n因為決定到你成唔成功係睇你對自己既諗法同期望<br />\n繼續做一個垃圾既角色係冇用<br />\n如果發現自己既paradigm 同你想成為既人係唔同既話<br />\n咁就需要一個paradigm shift <br />\n每日嘗試去催眠自己 同自己講自己想成為點既人 每日要做到咩 有咩目標etc<br />\n久需久之你就會改變你既諗法同習慣<br />\n你既人生正係掌握係你手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：唔相信determinism <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n所有發生係我地身上既野都可以由我地既控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以各位廢青唔好再自怨自艾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ceebb08a13090d96805ab0b6f0d90ca6ace1905","tid":164592,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T18:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44e22d77761e5dd732bf7ced1b5ef16a2fb533a","tid":164592,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T20:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d569a345da94310fc09d2eec03e0fba8a335c3f5","tid":164592,"uid":10090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T00:17:32.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ccfccdaa28b3d3ca1a45517a56f9e3adc7e65c","tid":164592,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T00:18:49.000Z","msg":"毒撚最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c061428306fda3c856beb10882b0553a305941","tid":164592,"uid":62675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d86343cba0df4451269f02146a5ea235e108a1c","tid":164592,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:14:33.000Z","msg":"Ching 講得好好<br />\n曾經係100%的咸魚<br />\n宜家係 99.9% 咸魚"},{"pid":"4cde45a08bd455c4cd73b7e702bd45fc3b75b5f8","tid":164592,"uid":38797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78a11c014e6d56767b5ce15f9a2a8ef0acfbd59","tid":164592,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有頭髮邊個想做癩痢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以唔洗做毒撚邊個想做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係因為咁<br />\n我地先應該改變自己既諗法<br />\n同自己講 xxx都可以咁有自信 點解我唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都可以有自信 可以唔洗做毒撚<br />\n踏出左第一步之後<br />\n你就會發現其實改變自己並唔難 係睇自己想定唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75f98b81f33cbb6f549088957c8d6cd067c331f","tid":164592,"ui